Sun Oct 17 13:57:44 1999  Greg J. Badros <gjb@cs.washington.edu> (on behalf of A. Vorobiev)

	Changes from Alexander Vorobiev to improve fvwm-eval handling for
	use with FvwmKb module: http://linuxfan.com/~sparrow/software.
	
	* winlist.scm: Make filter-only-except public
	
	* fvwm-eval.scm: Make extract-command be more sophisticated in
 	handling missing ] at end.  Fix "Current" command, implemented
 	"ChangeDecor" command.  Added `get-one-string-arg' helper.
	
	* fvwm-module.scm: Fixed uses of logior to (not (zero? (logand
 	type mask))).  This makes modules' selecting of the messages they
 	want to receive work properly. Added more debugging code.

