	* ui-constraints-gtk-toggle-menu.scm: Use spacing of 1 between
	constraint instances.  Use two-column table, with second column
	hboxes containing enable checkboxes AND the delete buttons.  Give
	that box right alignment so things line up better.  Give the whole 
