Wed Sep 29 23:09:12 1999  Greg J. Badros  <gjb@cs.washington.edu>

	* gnome-hints.scm: Added some commented out debugging.  Do not set 
	a window to be maximized when it is also set to be minimized (gmc
	desktop_icons are this way, and maximizing them was causing them
	to lose their y positioin -- all went to (0,0) in error).

