	* snap.scm: Added, from Danius Michaelides

	* style.scm: Lame doc for window-style.

	* menus-extras.scm: Make sorted-by-car-string public, since it is
	used by winlist.scm

	* ScwmButtons.scm: Use #!, !# style comments for some sample code.

